## Start here
1. Read `runbook.md` top-to-bottom; work Phase 0 ‚Üí 6.
2. Fill `scoping-checklist.md`.
3. Copy `connector-config.env.example` ‚Üí `.local/connector-config.env` and inject
   `{{APPROVAL_TOKEN_VAR}}` (host env only, never VCS).
4. Open `exception-spec.inkspec.html` and author the spec (Phase 2).

## What `{{GENERATOR}}` did NOT do
It stamped the **blank** board and the **seed** decks. It did **not** author the `<<TOKEN>>`
business values, did **not** run the export, and did **not** inject the approval token ‚Äî those
are your supervised, per-customer acts.
